pre_caption: This is a point-of-view shot from within the steel superstructure of a large bridge, looking down its length. Graffiti is visible on an overhead beam, and below, train tracks run down the center, flanked by roadways and pink railings. A subway train is positioned on the tracks, and the bright sunlight casts long, dramatic shadows across the entire structure.
